            "Sovereignty is not isolation — it's integrity. Your experience can light the way for others.",
          links: [
            { text: "Hall of Origin", href: "/hall-of-origin" },
            { text: "Infrastructure", href: "/infrastructure" },
          ],
        },
      },
      interactionStyle: {
        witness: {
          name: "Witness",
          title: "The Still Presence",
          description:
            "You connect through presence more than words. Your power is in stillness. You don't need to fill space to be in connection. You absorb, hold, and reflect back what you receive. Your attention is your gift.",
