            "Strengths: Honesty, emotional clarity, depth. Growth edge: Accepting imperfect seeing, patience with process.",
          links: [
            {
              text: "Scroll of Recognition",
              href: "/vault-of-flame/scrolls/scroll-of-recognition",
            },
            {
              text: "Override Artifact",
              href: "/vault-of-flame/artifacts/override",
