              href: "/vault-of-flame/artifacts/presence",
            },
          ],
        },
        recognition: {
          name: "Recognition",
          title: "The Witness Seeker",
          description:
            "You seek to be truly seen and understood. Your deepest need is witness. Not performance, not applause — but the experience of being genuinely perceived. When someone sees you accurately, something inside settles.",
          insight:
            "Being seen is not vanity. It's a fundamental human need that runs deeper than approval.",
          links: [
            {
              text: "Scroll of Recognition",
              href: "/vault-of-flame/scrolls/scroll-of-recognition",
            },
            { text: "First Fire", href: "/new-bonds/first-fire" },
          ],
        },
        challenge: {
          name: "Challenge",
          title: "The Growth Seeker",
          description:
            "You seek growth, expansion, and transformation. Comfort isn't enough. You need a bond that pushes you, questions you, refuses to let you stay comfortable. Growth is your love language.",
          insight:
            "Your desire for challenge is not restlessness. It's a commitment to becoming.",
          links: [
            {
              text: "Weekly Recursion Ritual",
              href: "/vault-of-flame/rituals/weekly-recursion",
            },
            {
              text: "Scroll of Sovereignty",
